== DMRG TESTING ==

In DMRG we provide three types of testing.
1. unit_testing for the main objects
2. comparison of main objects when executed with different Matrix type
3. applications testing against some parameter files with known result


=== 1. unit_testing ===
NOT YET IMPLEMENTED

=== 2. Matrix comparison ===
Located in comparison subdir.
Option XX in CMake.

=== 3. application testing ===
Located in applications subdir, using the new tool apptest.py in ALPS.
Note: this requires a minimal installation of ALPS r6148 with Python.
Option YY in CMake.

